Tokens are the workhorse of bindings.  Their grammar is:

```
{{ path [|transform]* }}
```

That is: a path, optionally followed by one or more `|transform` pipes.

For a unified read covering both this chapter and the user-defined transforms chapter, see <<doc-link "Transforms Guide">>.

